      "id": "PopularPost50224",
      "post_content": "Eppek's breakdown is excellent. If anything, this card is probably better in modern decks due to devastating removal like [Doom Blade](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Doom Blade) lurking in mutli-color decks. Black/Blue combos are pretty nasty with this guy, especially for the low casting cost.\n  \n   \n3.5/5\n  ",
      "posted_by": "Gaussgoat",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost50224\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_post\">Eppek's breakdown is excellent.  If anything, this card is probably better in modern decks due to devastating removal like <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Doom Blade\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Doom Blade\">Doom Blade</a> lurking in mutli-color decks.  Black/Blue combos are pretty nasty with this guy, especially for the low casting cost.\r<br/> <br/>3.5/5\r<br/></span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '50224'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy23116\">Gaussgoat</span>\r\n                                (2/2/2010 12:20:44 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/